# devops-for-the-horde

- **Central repo**: `config/master.yaml` is the manifest; keep `README.md` and `docs/index.html` aligned when repos or domains change.
- **Visuals**: Glass-morphism (blur, translucent panels, subtle borders), dark base, Horde green accents — inspired by modern “glass” UI; do not copy proprietary product pixels.
- **IP**: Warcraft flavor in text only; **no** Blizzard game assets or ripped art.
- **Imagery**: Royalty-free stock only; keep attribution in `docs/index.html` when required.
